Packages 
Package Description
com.mojang.datafixers
Provides most of the classes you will be directly interacting with.

Provides functions for interacting with data/optics.
com.mojang.datafixers.kinds
Provides the kinds of data.
com.mojang.datafixers.optics
Provides the backend optics.
com.mojang.datafixers.optics.profunctors
Provides the backend Profunctor Optics
com.mojang.datafixers.schemas
Provides the base Schema class used to create new Schemas.
com.mojang.datafixers.types
Provides the different data type foundation used for schemas and datafixes.
com.mojang.datafixers.types.constant
Provides basic types for data.
com.mojang.datafixers.types.families
Provides the foundations for families of types.
com.mojang.datafixers.types.templates
Provides the factories or templates to build types.
com.mojang.datafixers.util
Provides utils for interacting with the kinds package.
